This package — both its source code and its bundled SVG icon assets — is
distributed under the terms of the Digital Agency of Japan's
"Illustration & Icon Materials Terms of Use", which is based on the
Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International License (CC BY 4.0).

The icon assets are derived from the Digital Agency's
"Illustration & Icon Materials" (デジタル庁 イラストレーション・アイコン素材).
The surrounding code (Web Component implementation, build scripts, type
declarations, and tests) is provided under the same terms so that the
